snippet.title: Longplay of ClayFighter: Tournament Edition
snippet.description:
Longplay of ClayFighter: Tournament Edition, played as the NTSC version on the Super Nintendo Entertainment System. This game's version was released on May 15th, 1994. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!
